[[File:Sunset_Peak.JPG|thumb]]望向大東山，可見依山而建的爛頭營和山頂的[[三角網測站|三角網測站]]]]
大嶼山總面積達146.75平方公里，是香港最大的島嶼，位處香港西南面，在珠江三角洲口。大嶼山上香港第二及第三高的山嶺，分別是[[鳳凰山_(香港)|鳳凰山]]（934米）及[[大東山|大東山]]（869米）。大嶼山的主要海灣有[[東涌灣|東涌灣]]、[[陰澳灣|陰澳灣]]、[[大白灣|大白灣]]、[[銀礦灣|銀礦灣]]、[[貝澳灣|貝澳灣]]、[[芝麻灣|芝麻灣]]、[[水口灣|水口灣]]、[[分流東灣|分流東灣]]和[[分流西灣|分流西灣]]。

地質方面，大嶼山的岩石以[[火成岩|火成岩]]為主，大嶼山東部有很多[[花崗岩|花崗岩]]。[[石英二長岩|石英二長岩]]則見於大嶼山南部的[[塘福|塘福]]、[[梅窩|梅窩]]、[[貝澳|貝澳]]等地。<ref name="hkh4">{{cite web | language= | publisher= | title=香港植物名錄 | url=http://www.hkherbarium.net/herbarium/PDF/Chinese%20Check%20List%20Prelim_Intro.pdf | author= | date= | accessdate= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060528060101/http://www.hkherbarium.net/herbarium/PDF/Chinese%20Check%20List%20Prelim_Intro.pdf | archive-date=2006-05-28 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

大部分香港有記錄的物種類都在大嶼山，包括：70%的兩棲類及爬蟲類、60%的蜻蜓、55%的蝴蝶及超過50%的淡水魚類。好像大嶼山以北海域則是[[中華白海豚|中華白海豚]]經常出沒的地方，<ref name="afcd">{{cite web | language= | publisher=漁農自然護理署 | title=最常見的海豚 | url=http://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/conservation/con_mar/con_mar_chi/con_mar_chi_dol/dolphin_search_result.asp?discover_place=NL | author= | date= | accessdate= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150501185948/http://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/conservation/con_mar/con_mar_chi/con_mar_chi_dol/dolphin_search_result.asp?discover_place=NL | archive-date=2015-05-01 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>但是卻面對機場所帶來的種種威脅，如污水處理、生境地喪失、航行船隻增加。<ref name="wwf">{{cite web |language= |publisher=世界自然(香港)基金 |title=中華白海豚 |url=http://www.wwf.org.hk/chi/pdf/references/factsheets/factsheet14.PDF |author= |date= |accessdate= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071010233556/http://www.wwf.org.hk/chi/pdf/references/factsheets/factsheet14.PDF |archivedate=2007-10-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>大嶼山的西南部則是[[黃斑弄蝶|黃斑弄蝶]]過冬的勝地。<ref name="ecotour">{{cite web | language= | publisher=成報 | title=大嶼山是蝴蝶過冬勝地 | url=http://www.ecotourism.org.hk/other%20files/News/SingPao_190205.htm | author= | date= | accessdate= | archive-date=2008-09-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080917105807/http://www.ecotourism.org.hk/other%20files/News/SingPao_190205.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>

大嶼山境內有很多不同種類的植物，譬如[[香港細辛|香港細辛]]<ref name="hkh1">{{cite web | language= | publisher=Hong Kong Herbarium | title=香港細辛Asarum hongkongense | url=http://www.hkherbarium.net/Herbarium/html%20text/21Asarum%20hongkongense.htm | author= | date= | accessdate= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080928072500/http://www.hkherbarium.net/Herbarium/html%20text/21Asarum%20hongkongense.htm | archive-date=2008-09-28 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[石梓|石梓]]<ref name="hkh2">{{cite web | language= | publisher=Hong Kong Herbarium | title=Gmelina chinensis | url=http://www.hkherbarium.net/herbarium/html%20text/41Gmelina%20chinensis.htm | author= | date= | accessdate= | archive-date=2009-05-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090520054508/http://www.hkherbarium.net/Herbarium/html%20text/41Gmelina%20chinensis.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[毛葉杜鵑|毛葉杜鵑]]<ref>{{cite web | language= | publisher=Hong Kong Herbarium | title=毛葉杜鵑Rhododendron championae | url=http://www.hkherbarium.net/Herbarium/html%20text/68Rhododendron%20championae.htm | author= | date= | accessdate= | archive-date=2005-04-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050407025001/http://www.hkherbarium.net/Herbarium/html%20text/68Rhododendron%20championae.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[藤石松|藤石松]]、[[二形卷柏|二形卷柏]]、[[綠毛卷柏|綠毛卷柏]]、[[細葉卷柏|細葉卷柏]]、[[疏葉卷柏|疏葉卷柏]]、[[狹葉紫萁|狹葉紫萁]]、[[粵紫萁|粵紫萁]]、[[華南紫萁|華南紫萁]]、[[中華裏白|中華裏白]]、[[露蕨|露蕨]]、[[小果露蕨|小果露蕨]]、[[長柄露蕨|長柄露蕨]]、[[刺桫欏|刺桫欏]]、[[日本金粉蕨|日本金粉蕨]]、[[鞭葉鐵線蕨|鞭葉鐵線蕨]]、[[鐮葉鐵角蕨|鐮葉鐵角蕨]]、[[鐮羽貫眾|鐮羽貫眾]]、[[陰石蕨|陰石蕨]]等等。<ref name="hkh3">{{cite web | language= | publisher=Hong Kong Herbarium | title=Ferns Gymnos | url=http://www.hkherbarium.net/herbarium/PDF/Chi%20part1_Ferns_Gymnos.pdf | author= | date= | accessdate= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111019092217/http://www.hkherbarium.net/herbarium/PDF/Chi%20part1_Ferns_Gymnos.pdf | archive-date=2011-10-19 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>當中[[香港細辛|香港細辛]]、[[大嶼八角|大嶼八角]]、[[嶺南槭|嶺南槭]]更是首次在大嶼山發現。<ref name="hkh5">{{cite web | language= | publisher=Hong Kong Herbarium |